column5: Well today was very interesting afte the crazy storms we had last night! Made for a very slow and painful fish until this big guy was hauled Ito the boat    This sow was 5.4 on the tournament scales.... Wasn't even enough for me to win big fish for the day NEXT TIME!
Walleye-man?.......that's a bass.  Just sayin.......  S.
Sounds like some real big fish water.  Nice one!
